      <title>哈里斯在摇摆州巡回演讲后在旧金山举行募捐活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/harris-follows-swing-state-tour-with-fundraiser-in-san-francisco</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选团队表示，在摇摆州巡回介绍竞选搭档蒂姆·沃尔兹之后，她在其政治大本营旧金山招募捐款者，在加州高层民主党人士出席的一场活动中筹集了 1200 多万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/harris-follows-swing-state-tour-with-fundraiser-in-san-francisco</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 21:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯军队向其占领的核电站开火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/ukraine-says-russian-army-starts-fire-at-occupied-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，俄罗斯军队在乌克兰南部被占领的扎波罗热核电站内纵火，他呼吁国际社会和国际原子能机构作出反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/ukraine-says-russian-army-starts-fire-at-occupied-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 20:13:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗通讯社称伊朗总统与欧盟代表米歇尔讨论加沙问题和核协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-s-president-eu-s-michel-talk-gaza-nuclear-deal-irna-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统就以色列对加沙的战争向一位欧洲高级官员发出警告，同时也表示德黑兰方面愿意重启 2015 年核协议谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-s-president-eu-s-michel-talk-gaza-nuclear-deal-irna-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约旦国王呼吁缓和地区紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/jordan-s-king-calls-for-de-escalation-of-tensions-in-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约旦国王阿卜杜拉二世呼吁缓和中东紧张局势，防止爆发全面的地区战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/jordan-s-king-calls-for-de-escalation-of-tensions-in-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 16:50:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯支持减免 5,000 美元儿童税，以稳定竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/vance-backs-5-000-child-tax-credit-in-bid-to-steady-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党副总统候选人 JD Vance 提出将联邦儿童税收抵免额增加一倍以上至 5,000 美元，试图重塑受到民主党攻击的“亲家庭”立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/vance-backs-5-000-child-tax-credit-in-bid-to-steady-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:13:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称退出竞选是因为担心会“分散注意力”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/biden-says-he-dropped-out-because-he-feared-being-distraction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，在听闻国会民主党人表示他将损害他们在 11 月的选举机会后，他结束了竞选连任的竞选活动，并对他退出的决定提供了迄今为止最全面的解释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/biden-says-he-dropped-out-because-he-feared-being-distraction</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 14:19:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赞比亚关闭与刚果的边境，阻断关键铜贸易路线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/zambia-closes-border-with-congo-blocking-key-copper-trade-route</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚政府周末表示，已暂时关闭与刚果民主共和国的边境，此举可能会导致非洲最大铜生产国的出口延迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/zambia-closes-border-with-congo-blocking-key-copper-trade-route</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 13:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强基础设施防御以抵御伊朗威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/israel-bolsters-infrastructure-defense-amid-iranian-attack-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果人们需要进入避难所，市长们准备好了电池供电的警报器，急救人员准备好了卫星电话和老式晶体管收音机，它们可以成为信息生命线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/israel-bolsters-infrastructure-defense-amid-iranian-attack-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 13:37:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方逮捕在闭幕式前数小时攀爬埃菲尔铁塔的男子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-11/urgent-a-man-is-seen-climbing-the-eiffel-tower-prompting-an-evacuation-hours-before-closing-ceremony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴黎（美联社）——周日奥运会闭幕式前几个小时，有人看到一名男子攀爬巴黎地标建筑埃菲尔铁塔，随后法国警方疏散了该区域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-11/urgent-a-man-is-seen-climbing-the-eiffel-tower-prompting-an-evacuation-hours-before-closing-ceremony</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 13:28:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统佩泽什基安在以色列紧张局势升温之际任命内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-s-pezeshkian-names-cabinet-amid-simmering-israel-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗改革派总统马苏德·佩泽什基安选择了 2015 年核协议的设计者之一担任外交部长，并选择了一位业内资深人士担任石油行业最高职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-s-pezeshkian-names-cabinet-amid-simmering-israel-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 11:13:16 GMT</pubDate>
